heading { level = 1, Metadata API }

The metadata API endpoint can be used to get the sync status of your sync tasks.
To get this info, make a GET request to the following URL, replacing
\{TASK_ID\} with your task ID.

code {
  https://api.kenshi.io/index/info/\{TASK_ID\}
}

heading { level = 2, Example response }

code {
  \{"lastSyncedBlock":12755853\}
}
